job.description:
SRE&amp;nbsp;– (Remote) - Up to&amp;nbsp;$200,000 +&amp;nbsp;10%&amp;nbsp;+ Benefits/Shares&amp;nbsp;   One of the market leaders&amp;nbsp;in producing&amp;nbsp;Blockchain&amp;nbsp;software&amp;nbsp;solutions&amp;nbsp;is looking&amp;nbsp;for an SRE with strong skills&amp;nbsp;within a&amp;nbsp;managed production environment, especially with&amp;nbsp;Kubernetes.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;The company was&amp;nbsp;set up&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;co-founder&amp;nbsp;of Ethereum&amp;nbsp;in 2014 and since then,&amp;nbsp;they have grown to become one of the&amp;nbsp;world's&amp;nbsp;best-recognised&amp;nbsp;Ethereum solutions&amp;nbsp;companies. Located in 30&amp;nbsp;different&amp;nbsp;countries,&amp;nbsp;open to remote working&amp;nbsp;across&amp;nbsp;the U.S&amp;nbsp;with a great level of engineering.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Key Benefits&amp;nbsp;  - 100% Remote &amp;nbsp;   
  - Unlimited holidays&amp;nbsp;   
  - Learn&amp;nbsp;about deploying onto Blockchain&amp;nbsp;(Ethereum)&amp;nbsp;infrastructure&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;   
  - Join an industry that is developing&amp;nbsp;every&amp;nbsp;day&amp;nbsp;   
  - Be part of greenfield DevOps Blockchain projects&amp;nbsp;   
  - 10% Bonus + Equity&amp;nbsp;   
&amp;nbsp;As one of the company’s&amp;nbsp;SRE’s, you will have a great opportunity to make a huge impact on the engineering function of the team,&amp;nbsp;define and manage all aspects of the development and production infrastructure.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;   Responsibilities:&amp;nbsp;  - Continuously improve team’s processes, tools and solutions used to build, deploy, monitor, maintain and scale production systems&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;   
  - Improve the monitoring, alerting and remediation solutions and proactively identify production issues&amp;nbsp;   
  - Lead efforts to remediate critical operational platform issues&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;   
  - Design and improve support processes in collaboration with support and dev teams&amp;nbsp;   
   Required skills, not limited to:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;  - Linux&amp;nbsp;Engineering&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;   
  - Scripting -&amp;nbsp;Python,&amp;nbsp;Bash, Go&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;   
  - Cloud (AWS/GCP/Azure)&amp;nbsp;   
  - Monitoring – ELK,&amp;nbsp;Prometheus&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;   
  - Infrastructure as Code - Terraform (Preferred)&amp;nbsp;   
  - CI/CD - Jenkins&amp;nbsp;   
  - Kubernetes&amp;nbsp;   
&amp;nbsp;Please apply below or contact Emmanuel&amp;nbsp;Oloko at&amp;nbsp;emmanuel@chisquare-analytics.com&amp;nbsp;or call 07546110052 for a confidential chat.&amp;nbsp;
